{"type":"text","timestamp":1775891709087,"sessionID":"ses_2849bfcc3ffeMnzI8RQVHE0I1w","part":{"id":"prt_d7b64f9d3001lyg7W2kfMBmCKh","messageID":"msg_d7b64d43f001VJ3ZSqbmKa3ok4","sessionID":"ses_2849bfcc3ffeMnzI8RQVHE0I1w","type":"text","text":"Now I have a comprehensive understanding of the codebase. Let me write the proposal for AR-023 - CLI invoke/status commands.","time":{"start":1775891709086,"end":1775891709086}}}
